5:
Through you we will push down our adversaries;
\q through your name we will tread them under, those who rise up against us.
\q

10:
You make us turn back from the adversary;
\q and those who hate us take spoil for themselves.
\q

12:
You sell your people for nothing;
\q you have not increased your wealth by doing so.
\q

18:
Our heart has not turned back;
\q our steps have not gone from your way.
\q

25:
For we have melted away into the dust;
\q our bodies cling to the earth.
\q
